Careers









  




JB Capital is looking for bright, accomplished professionals. If you are interested in a position with us, please email your resume and cover letter to info@jb-capital.com




//Director
As a Director of JB Capital, your task will be to assist in the discovery and development of capital sources and new potential client engagements. Position will have a significant involvement in transactions from origination through closing, and must be able to exhibit the ability to work on multiple projects and transactions concurrently.  Experience should include:

Business Development/Origination Experience in markets served by JB Capital
Ability to oversee and lead execution team
3 Years + Experience in Investment Banking, Commercial Finance or Private Equity





//Associate
As an Associate of JB Capital, your task will be to assist in the discovery and development of capital sources and new potential client engagements. Position will be involved with transactions from inception to completion. Candidate will work with and support Senior Leadership on engagements must have ability to work on multiple projects and transactions concurrently.  Experience should include:

Business Development/Origination Experience in markets served by JB Capital
Client focused, results oriented, self-motivated work ethic
1 Year + Experience in Investment Banking, Commercial Finance Or Private Equity





