Our Company









  




JB Capital is a privately held investment banking and commercial finance company. Combining broad industry expertise and transaction experience, we offer independent, professional advice to privately held companies.
For over ten years, focusing solely on providing businesses with access to conventional and alternative debt markets, we have been the leading broker of capital for businesses throughout the Northwest. 








   
